      "value": "<p>You can spend 10 minutes inspiring your companions, shoring up their resolve to fight. When you do so, choose up to your Proficiency Bonus friendly creatures other than yourself within 30 feet of you who can see or hear you and who can understand you. Each creature can gain Temporary Hit Points equal to your level + your Charisma modifier. If at least one creature gains Temporary Hit Points in this way then so can you. A creature cannot gain Temporary Hit Points from this feat again until it has finished a Short or Long Rest.</p>",
